                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070218-15-off80 t18070218-15-cd81"></join>, twenty nine pound weight and a half of copper, value 2 l
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18070218-15-victim234" type="victimName">
                     Owen 
                     Williams
